<p><strong>作品名称：</strong>老屋</p>
<p><strong>类型：</strong>Creepypasta / GoI格式 - “观缪维基”</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pokm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662223); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3662223&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601032202" alt="pokm" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3662223)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pokm" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662223); return false;">pokm</a></span></p>
